{"tid":1850270,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改歌】武漢爆肺炎哇 中央的指令不准走哇","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:55:30.000Z","uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0077ae4fe3caa024e54137886c66a677d69653","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NftHOzQbJ1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNftHOzQbJ1Y&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=df3ce883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NftHOzQbJ1Y</a><br />\n<br />\n(國語)武漢歌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">武漢爆肺炎哇<br />\n中央的指令不准走哇<br />\n（嘿 嘿 不准走哇）<br />\n（生死之間沒人救哇）<br />\n<br />\n說走咱就走哇<br />\n你有我有全都有哇<br />\n（嘿 嘿 全都有哇）<br />\n（武漢肺炎全國走哇）<br />\n<br />\n特區政府不封關哇</span><br />\n該出手時就出手哇<br />\n風風火火闖九州哇<br />\n（該出手時就出手哇）<br />\n（風風火火闖九州哇）<br />\n嘿兒呀 咿兒呀 嘿唉嘿依兒呀<br />\n（嘿兒呀 咿兒呀 嘿嘿嘿嘿依兒呀）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首歌好有神舟大地黃土地氣息，想送俾上面一時落魄人人喊打嘅同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望改得豪邁啲，表達武漢壯士勇闖天下嘅英雄氣蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f136f8d89e2be2f36343e85200fe04b282e2a2","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"原版歌詞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n大河向東流哇<br />\n天上的星星參北斗哇<br />\n（嘿 嘿 參北斗哇）<br />\n（生死之交一碗酒哇）<br />\n<br />\n說走咱就走哇<br />\n你有我有全都有哇<br />\n（嘿 嘿 全都有哇）<br />\n（水里火裡不回頭哇）<br />\n<br />\n路見不平一聲吼哇<br />\n該出手時就出手哇<br />\n風風火火闖九州哇<br />\n（該出手時就出手哇）<br />\n（風風火火闖九州哇）<br />\n嘿兒呀 咿兒呀 嘿唉嘿依兒呀<br />\n（嘿兒呀 咿兒呀 嘿嘿嘿嘿依兒呀）</span>"},{"pid":"3ab253b7cb3a7079ee57ca4aafd129fb611090da","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"btw返開路德會，唔知啱唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4b7a10b6f3eb97922ddd7ef7f8543c1ebbce8a","tid":1850270,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eY8gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eY8gq.jpg&h=286709db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7e9a2ffae0ac29f936e17f6639ca624df5a1b8","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4b7a10b6f3eb97922ddd7ef7f8543c1ebbce8a","tid":1850270,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eY8gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eY8gq.jpg&h=286709db&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da55dea939c77a4c78de60b8b8b253916d00377","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab487d72d7d51f1fb55f6d2ae8184b3450da6046","tid":1850270,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}